Middleware:

Middleware is a function that take an action and depending on the actions type and the action payload or any other number of factor.

Middleware can choose to let the action pass through before hitting the reducer and manipulate the action.

Middleware has the ability to block modify or just let pass through actions as they created before they hit reducer.

package: https://www.npmjs.com/package/redux-promise

